comment.text: This translation key is used to display a label for a filter option in a UI component, specifically in a file management system or media library. It indicates which type of files are being filtered (e.g., presentations), and its purpose is to provide context for users navigating the file selection process.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Sinhala translation "සමර්පණ" is a plausible attempt but not the most common or accurate translation of "Presentations". It leans towards "offerings" or "submissions" rather than a formal presentation.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider "ප්‍රස්ථාවතා" (prasthāvatā) or " ඉදිරිපත් කිරීම්" (idiriipath kirim) for a more accurate translation of 'Presentations'.
